n></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p>其中：</p>
<ul>
<li>j：算法编号</li>
<li>i：实例编号</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h3 id="step-3-计算-friedman-统计量" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#step-3-计算-friedman-统计量"><span>Step 3：计算 Friedman 统计量</span></a></h3>
<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><msubsup><mi>χ</mi><mi>F</mi><mn>2</mn></msubsup><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>12</mn><mi>N</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>k</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>k</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mfrac><mrow><mo fence="true">[</mo><munderover><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mi>j</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mi>k</mi></munderover><msubsup><mover accent="true"><mi>R</mi><mo>ˉ</mo></mover><mi>j</mi><mn>2</mn></msubsup><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>k</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>k</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><msup><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mo fence="true">]</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\chi_F^2 = 
\frac{12N}{k(k+1)}
\left[
